  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA185-kiḷavi">1. itu pāṅkaṟkut talaivaṉ colliyatu.
            2. cēṭpaṭukkun tōḻikkut talaivaṉ colliyatūumām.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">1. This is what HE said to [his] companion.
            2. It is also what HE said to the confidante who kept [him] at a distance.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA185">
<l>            āṉā nōyō ṭaḻipaṭark kalaṅkik</l>
<l>            kāmaṅ kaimmikak kaiyaṟu tuyaraṅ</l>
<l>            kāṇavu nalkā yāyiṟ pāṇar</l>
<l>            paricil peṟṟa viriyuḷai naṉmāṉ</l>
<l>            kavikuḷampu poruta kaṉmicaic ciṟuneṟi </l>
<l>            yiravalar meliyā tēṟum poṟaiya</l>
<l>            ṉuraicā luyarvaraik kollik kuṭavayi</l>
<l>            ṉakalilaik kānta ḷalaṅkukulaip pāyntu</l>
<l>            paṟavai yiḻaitta palka ṇiṟāaṟ</l>
<l>            ṟēṉuṭai neṭuvarait teyva meḻutiya </l>
<l>            viṉaimāṇ pāvai yaṉṉōḷ</l>
<l>            kolaicūḻn taṉaḷā ṉōkō yāṉē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent3">With unending pain, perturbed by destructive affliction,</l>
<l rend="indent3">in motionless misery, while desire exceeds,</l>
<l rend="indent">– if you don't grant even seeing [her],</l>
<l>she has indeed planned to kill [me],</l>
<l rend="indent">she who is like the gloriously crafted image</l>
<l rend="indent3">drawn by the god on the long mountain full of honey,</l>
<l rend="indent2">in many-eyed honeycombs made by bees,</l>
<l rend="indent2">spreading on the swaying bunches of wide-leaved Malabar-lilies,</l>
<l rend="indent">on the west side of Kolli, the praise-worthy high mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">of the Poṟaiyaṉ, where the beggars ascend without weakening</l>
<l rend="indent2">on the small paths in stony height struck by the broad hoofs</l>
<l rend="indent2">of broad-maned good horses, obtained as a gift by the bards.</l>
<l rend="indent4">Ah, I ache.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
        </text>
